name: Cafe Jazz

reviews.review_text: The place is awesome , just like it's ambience, music , food. The quantity and quality of the food is too good. The place is situated on the main road of Candolim just opposite of Delfinio's Supermarket
We loved the food including authentic Goan cuisines, roti , bread . Butter garlic mushroom , tandoor chicken , Goan balchao with poie best .
Great experience dining here. Food was good. Live music was awesome

description:
**Café Jazz: A Culinary Retreat in Goa**  

Nestled in the vibrant heart of Candolim, Café Jazz stands out as a dining gem with an impressive rating of 4.2 based on over 2,300 reviews. This lively establishment has garnered attention for its enchanting ambience, delectable food offerings, and pulsating evening crowd, making it a perfect spot for both locals and tourists seeking a captivating dining experience.

**Ambiance & Design**  
As you step into Café Jazz, you're immediately enveloped by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The décor strikes a perfect balance between rustic charm and contemporary flair, enhanced by a thoughtful lighting scheme that creates an intimate setting for patrons. Customers have noted the vibe is punctuated by lively music, which plays a central role in the overall experience. Details from the reviews suggest that the restaurant is often bustling with life, particularly in the evenings, turning it into a hotspot for those looking to unwind and enjoy a fantastic meal while soaking in the tunes.

![Café Jazz Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmwGJ16xsC4MPKW_Ers6xDKAacN0aYxkFzAOs1JpZsaLNgOGMoqPUVgn2_G1eX_4XMOahJYpDIq0RuYLq1E1o6DoJM494-6VGyHt6FPKEg2aKl8P5ckz0ofFE_qenO_xEGsYkKs9g=w375-h281-p)  

**Menu & Culinary Experience**  
Café Jazz prides itself on a diverse menu that expertly showcases the flavors of Goa. Signature dishes include the Butter Garlic Mushroom and Tandoor Chicken, praised for their taste and generous portions. Authentic Goan cuisine, such as Balchao served with traditional poie (Goan bread), takes center stage, allowing diners to experience the local culinary heritage. The food presentation is both appealing and homely, making it a treat for the eyes as well as the palate. Vegetarian options are also available, ensuring inclusivity for all diners.

![Goan Cuisine at Café Jazz](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkV8F4YvIF9-thMsTFgcNPlb660v1UbMPQTnIBTSbn0dGh5RTNrKl4SgGgE9XM_3kBX6JLabuA_fFtVCnmkapNwtSgwYcCBE7IxxVna_2zWv2036Hhua8_LyWVBhjD7yy9vKjZ7_Q=w375-h563-p)  

**Customer Experience & Service**  
The service at Café Jazz has received notable commendations from guests. Reviews reflect a staff that is not only friendly and attentive but also knowledgeable about the menu, enhancing the overall dining experience. Many visitors recommend making reservations, especially during peak hours, as this bustling restaurant can quickly fill up with eager diners looking to enjoy an evening of great music and food.

**Popularity & Reviews**  
The buzz around Café Jazz is palpable, with patrons frequently highlighting the live music as a standout feature that elevates the dining experience. Social media posts often depict lively evenings filled with music and laughter, inviting others to join in on the fun. With a steady influx of positive reviews, it is clear that this café has carved a niche for itself as a must-visit destination for both locals and tourists alike.

![Dining Experience at Café Jazz](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnJZgBR77wvHqQoN7LoGId19VZOvYuU3RfiGjiEE-Ut1AO-9md4_HKGHKaiETlbVrHPUkXLWS90hJ3CCiq8cLibkeHf1OPxke_tPoCCKxeZT6zBt_N2-7U1VrXbp2SBDFlwp1h3=w375-h281-p)  

In conclusion, Café Jazz is more than just a dining establishment; it’s a vibrant experience that resonates with the spirit of Goa. With its captivating ambience, eclectic menu, and fantastic live music, it is definitely a place worth exploring for anyone looking to savor the essence of this beautiful coastal state. Whether you're dining with friends, a special someone, or simply enjoying a night out, Café Jazz promises an unforgettable culinary journey.
